<MethodEndpoint
  method={"get"}
  path={"/receiver/data/v2/financings/contracts/warranties/{consentPactualId}/{contractId}"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



Endpoint that our client must call to get the information from Open Finance:
    
* Open Finance endpoint that will be requested: ```(GET /contracts/{contractId}/warranties)```
    
* FamilyType: ```Operações de Crédito - Financiamento``` 
    
The response content provided by this endpoint uses the same entity as the provided on the [Open Banking Brazil Oficial Documentation](https://openfinancebrasil.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OF/pages/474415286/Informa+es+T+cnicas+-+DC+Financiamento+-+v2.2.0).
